; Coverage test for xact.cc lines 595,597,612-615
; Tests balanced virtual postings with null amounts.
; The virtual_null_post path handles balancing [bracketed] virtual postings
; separately from regular postings. This tests the is_amount() path for
; virtual_balance when auto-calculating a null virtual posting.

2024/01/01 Test balanced virtual
    Expenses:Food              $50.00
    Assets:Cash
    [Budget:Food]              $50.00
    [Budget:Savings]

test bal
             $-50.00  Assets:Cash
                   0  Budget
              $50.00    Food
             $-50.00    Savings
              $50.00  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
end test
